author: Haris Alic
title: Top Biden Adviser Repeatedly Referred to Coronavirus as ‘Wuhan Virus’
description: A top adviser to Joe Biden repeatedly described the Coronavirus as "Wuhan virus" earlier this year, around the same time the former vice president was castigating political opponents for doing likewise.
